
MolecularMap (root)
│
├── index.html         → Homepage
│   ├─ Hero section (AI-first positioning)
│   ├─ Stats (100M+ molecules target, 1B+ relationships target)
│   ├─ Features (disease search, curation, relationships, sonification, AI)
│   ├─ Graph demo (cytoscape.js)
│   ├─ Call-to-action (Academic vs. Commercial datasets)
│   └─ Footer (Patents, links, © 2014–2024)
│
├── about.html         → About Page
│   ├─ Mission
│   ├─ History (founded 2014, growth, AI-first vision)
│   ├─ Patents & IP (2 awarded + pending portfolio)
│   ├─ Vision (ImageNet analogy, multimodality, sonification)
│   └─ Footer links
│
├── datasets.html      → Datasets Page
│   ├─ Intro (academic free, commercial licensed)
│   ├─ Academic Access (download sample dataset)
│   ├─ Commercial Licensing (request via email)
│   ├─ Future Releases (100M+, pathways, spectra, ancient medicine)
│   └─ Footer links
│
├── contribute.html    → Contribute Data Page
│   ├─ What You Can Contribute (structures, pathways, spectra, disease links)
│   ├─ Guidelines (academic vs. commercial)
│   ├─ Contribution Form (mailto:contribute@molecularmap.com)
│   └─ Footer links
│
├── api.html           → Developers / API Page
│   ├─ Planned Features (REST queries, graph queries, ML-ready exports)
│   ├─ Data Formats (JSON, RDF, Neo4j, CSV)
│   ├─ Example Queries (GET /api/molecule, /api/pathways, /api/dataset)
│   ├─ “Coming Soon” Box (early access contact)
│   └─ Footer links
│
├── search.php         → Search Page (future vertical AI agent)
│   ├─ Input box (from homepage hero)
│   ├─ Meta-search (Google, PubChem, ChEMBL, UniProt, KEGG, PubMed, etc.)
│   └─ Future: replace with MolecularMap’s internal AI-curated graph
│
├── /downloads/        → Folder for sample datasets
│   └─ molecularmap-sample.zip (example)
│
├── /static/           → Assets folder
│   └─ molecularmap-preview.png (OpenGraph/Twitter preview image)
│
├── /privacy           → Privacy Policy (placeholder)
└── /license           → Dataset License (placeholder)

